---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();

const categories = [
  { name: 'Carti si Dictionare', slug: 'carti-si-dictionare' },
  { name: 'Invatare Limbi Straine', slug: 'invatare-limbi-straine' },
  { name: 'Electronice Educative', slug: 'electronice-educative' },
  { name: 'Jocuri de Cuvinte', slug: 'jocuri-de-cuvinte' }
];
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"/>
          </svg>
          DictionarulTau.ro
        </h3>
        <p>Resurse complete pentru invatarea limbilor straine, dictionare de calitate si materiale educative. Iti oferim ghiduri detaliate pentru a-ti imbunatati vocabularul si abilitatile lingvistice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Categorii</h4>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          {categories.map(cat => (
            <li><a href={`/${cat.slug}/`}>{cat.name}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Legal</h4>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/privacy-policy/">Politica de Confidentialitate</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms/">Termeni si Conditii</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cookies/">Politica Cookies</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Utile</h4>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sitemap/">Harta Site</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://ofertatelefoane.ro/">Top Telefoane 2026</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} DictionarulTau.ro. Toate drepturile rezervate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
